'''蓋·魯伯特·貝瑞曼'''（{{lang-en|Guy Rupert Berryman}}，{{bd|1978年|4月12日}}），生於[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[柯科迪|柯科迪]]，是英國[[另類搖滾|另類搖滾]]樂團[[酷玩樂團|酷玩樂團]]的[[貝斯吉他|貝斯手]]。

== 私人生活 ==
貝瑞曼畢業於[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]的私立[[愛丁堡學院|愛丁堡學院]]與[[肯特郡|肯特郡]]的[[肯特郡坎特伯里學院|肯特郡坎特伯里學院]]，隨後進入[[倫敦大學學院|倫敦大學學院]]就讀。2004年，貝瑞曼與青梅竹馬喬安娜·布里斯頓結婚<ref>{{cite web|first=Daniel|last=Killkelly|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/a46475/coldplay-star-splits-from-wife.html|title=Coldplay star splits from wife|accessdate=2008-07-11|date=2007-05-12|publisher=Digital Spy|archive-date=2012-04-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66guA3pcy?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a46475/coldplay-star-splits-from-wife.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[西敏市|西敏市]]低調舉行了典禮。他們育有一女妮可，其出生於2006年9月17日<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1542172/20061002/coldplay.jhtml|title=No Five-Year Hiatus For Coldplay — But They Are Taking A Break|last=Montgomery|first=James|date=2006-10-02|work=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|publisher=''mtv.com'' ([[MTV|MTV Networks]])|accessdate=2008-10-14|archive-date=2009-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091130180706/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1542172/20061002/coldplay.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://breakingnews.iol.ie/entertainment/story.asp?j=197123672&p=y97yz4378|title=Coldplay to take hiatus?|accessdate=2008-07-11|date=2006-10-02|publisher=Ireland On-Line|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68IH0jfFX?url=http://www.breakingnews.ie/entertainment/cwqlsncwkfcw/?from=iol|archivedate=2012年6月9日|df=}}</ref>。2007年3月，酷玩樂團的發言人證實蓋已與喬安娜離婚，結束三年的婚姻，但仍為妮可建立幸福童年而頻繁接觸<ref>{{cite web|first=Chris|last=Taylor|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news?id=31578|title=Coldplay Star Splits With Wife|quote=Coldplay bassist Guy Berryman has split from his childhood sweetheart wife Joanna just six months after the birth of their first child|accessdate=2008-07-11|date=2007-05-12|publisher=Entertainment Wise|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822085548/http://entertainmentwise.com/news/?id=31578|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝瑞曼酷愛跑步，習慣在鄰近的公園或旅館四周慢跑。他也熱衷於攝影、時尚及一些小電子裝置<ref name=quiet>Scaggs, Austin; Corbijn, Anton (2005-08-25), "COLDPLAY'S QUIET STORM". ''Rolling Stone''. (981):40-46</ref>。

據2008年4月英國MSN上的一篇文章所載，貝瑞曼已有財產約2500萬英鎊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://money.uk.msn.com/guides/salarycentre/gallery.aspx?cp-documentid=7260461&dub-gallery-photo-number=7 |title=4 - Guy Berryman, £25 million - Salary centre<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129221227/http://money.uk.msn.com/guides/salarycentre/gallery.aspx?cp-documentid=7260461&dub-gallery-photo-number=7 |archive-date=2009-01-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2016年，他以5500万英镑资产位居英国最富有的音乐人第42位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11626386|title=Britain's top 50 Music Millionaires revealed|publisher=NZ Herald|date=2016-04-21|accessdate=2017-04-12|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803044334/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11626386|dead-url=no}}</ref>

